    <title>Flat Hunt User Guide</title>
    
    <para>
        <projectname>Flat Hunt</projectname> is an application that is used to teach you programming, along with another application named <projectname>Touch</projectname> [<link linkend="references">rk05</link>]. 
        <projectname>Flat Hunt</projectname> is a "Scotland Yard"-like game that will mainly appear in the assignments for the Introduction to Programming course.
        It is based on <libraryname>TRAFFIC</libraryname> [<link linkend="references">sa05</link>] for modeling the city where the game takes place and on <libraryname>EiffelMedia</libraryname> 
        (formerly known as <libraryname>ESDL</libraryname> [<link linkend="references">tgb03</link>]) for visualization.
    </para>
    
